about.summary: The agile query language for semi-structured data.

name: objectpath
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "objectpath" %}
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 461263136c79292e42431fbb85cdcaac4c6a256f6b1aa5b3ae9316e4965ad819

build:
  number: 0
  entry_points:
    - objectpath = objectpath.shell:main
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - wheel
  run:
    - python
    - pyreadline  # [win]
    - readline    # [not win]
    - pytz
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - objectpath
    - objectpath.core
    - objectpath.utils
  commands:
    - objectpath --help

about:
  home: http://adriank.github.io/ObjectPath
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: The agile query language for semi-structured data.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sp-hbk
    - pg-hbk
